"Alright, Talon and Ravenchief come with me.  Guardia can lead the entrance
team," said Perseus decisely, motioning for the trooper to back her up.
"Kenzo can stay in here with Tuscon, you can back up the entry team if
things get too hot for them."

Kenzo gave a casual salute, being more doctor than military, he still liked
to. Acknowledge  acknowlege his leader.  A moment later both teams geared up
and exited the control room.

On Jan 29, 2010 8:15 PM, "Sandy" <magicquartz@...> wrote:

Tucson had been resting a while since his battle injury and the thrill of
the first fight does not daunt his desire to go back out there and do it all
over again.

"I - really hate to miss out - on the fun.  Perhaps in a few hours I'll be
ready to take on another challenge.  But - for now.. Yeah... I - could use a
few hours of down time I suppose."

He smiles, pats Talon on the shoulder and lies back to try and repair his
systems by giving them a rest.
